title: New Keen sprites
content:
While going through some files on my old computer I found a bunch of keen fan games and got nostalgic. I played around in photoshop a little and came up with some new sprites. These show Keen using some sort of force field embedded in his wrist watch and a new slide dodge manuever he picked up from the ninjas on Vorticon IV

[img]http://www.lookwhatimade.com/keen.gif[/img]

hope you like!
